---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Makers Fellowship">
  <main class="space-y-40 mb-20 md:mb-40">
    <div class="dark:text-white flex flex-col gap-6 mt-40 mx-10 md:mx-40 lg:mx-80">
      <h1 class="font-bold text-3xl md:text-5xl mb-4">
        Makers Fellowship: Elite Selection Process and Exceptional Standards
      </h1>

      <p>
        Makers Fellowship stands as the premier talent incubator in Latin
        America, dedicated to cultivating the next generation of world-class
        entrepreneurs and innovators. Our rigorous selection process and
        exceptionally high standards ensure that only the most promising and
        accomplished individuals are admitted to our program.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-bold">1. Outstanding Achievements-Based Selection</h2>

      <p>
        Makers Fellowship employs a meticulous selection process that
        prioritizes candidates with demonstrable outstanding achievements in
        entrepreneurship, technology, and business leadership. We seek
        individuals who have:
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc list-inside flex flex-col gap-1">
        <li>Founded or co-founded innovative startups</li>
        <li>Developed groundbreaking technologies or products</li>
        <li>Received recognition from prestigious institutions or competitions</li>
        <li>Demonstrated exceptional leadership in their respective fields</li>
        <li>Contributed significantly to open-source projects or community
          initiatives</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        Our selection criteria go beyond academic qualifications, focusing on
        tangible accomplishments that set candidates apart as top 1% talents in
        their domains.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-bold">2. Evaluation by Recognized Industry Experts</h2>

      <p>
        The selection of Makers Fellows is conducted by a panel of the most
        influential and accomplished leaders in the Latin American startup
        ecosystem. Our evaluators include:
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc list-inside flex flex-col gap-1">
        <li><span class="font-semibold">Andrés Bilbao:</span> Co-Founder of Rappi</li>
        <li><span class="font-semibold">Simon Borrero:</span> CEO and Co-founder of Rappi</li>
        <li><span class="font-semibold">Daniel Vogel:</span> Co-founder of Bitso, leading cryptocurrency platform in
          Latin America
        </li>
        <li><span class="font-semibold">Lina Rottemberg:</span> Founder of Endeavor, champion of high-impact
          entrepreneurship
        </li>
        <li><span class="font-semibold">Florian Hagenbuch:</span> Co-founder of Loft, real estate technology
          visionary
        </li>
        <li><span class="font-semibold">Gabriel Vásquez:</span> Partner at Andreessen Horowitz (a16z), top-tier
          venture capitalist
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        These industry titans bring their vast experience and discerning eye to
        identify and select only the most exceptional candidates who show the
        potential to become future leaders of Latin America’s tech and business
        landscape.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-bold">3. Exclusivity and Competitive Acceptance Rate</h2>

      <p>
        Makers Fellowship prides itself on its extremely selective nature,
        maintaining an acceptance rate that rivals the most prestigious
        institutions globally:
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc list-inside flex flex-col gap-1">
        <li>
          We receive thousands of applications from across Latin America for
          each cohort
        </li>
        <li>
          Our acceptance rate is consistently below 1%, making it one of the
          most competitive programs in the region
        </li>
        <li>
          Only 20-30 individuals are selected for each cohort, ensuring an
          intimate and high-quality experience
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        This level of exclusivity ensures that every Maker is truly a top 1%
        talent, capable of driving significant impact and innovation in the
        global startup ecosystem.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-bold">Post-Program Opportunities</h2>

      <p>
        The caliber of Makers Fellows is further validated by their placements
        post-program. Our alumni consistently secure positions at the most
        innovative and fast-growing startups in Latin America, including:
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc list-inside flex flex-col gap-1">
        <li>Rappi</li>
        <li>Addi</li>
        <li>Frubana</li>
        <li>Truora</li>
        <li>Ontop</li>
        <li>Arkangel AI</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        These placements underscore the exceptional quality of our Fellows and
        the value that top companies place on the Makers Fellowship experience.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  .text-gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6dbfa4, #8695cb);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }
</style>
